Summary: Simple implementation of the generic Tree data structure
Group: Development/Ruby
License: MIT or Ruby
Url: http://rubytree.anupamsg.me/

BuildArch: noarch

Source: %pkgname-%version.tar

BuildRequires(pre): rpm-build-ruby
